author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-AstraZeneca CEO says prices for acquisitions these days pretty hefty
text:
July 30 AstraZeneca PLC CEO Pascal Soriot told analysts: * CEO says looking at deals but prices for acquisitions these days are "pretty
hefty" * CEO says he never said in December 2014 interview that long-term target of
$45 billion sales by 2023 was difficult to hit * For more news, please click here
